votebox.auditoriumverifierplugins

Class DagBuilder

  • java.lang.Object
    • votebox.auditoriumverifierplugins.DagBuilder
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    FastDAGBuilder

    public class DagBuilder
extends java.lang.Object
    A DAG builder incrementally accepts auditorium messages and builds a DAG which represents the timeline of them. At any point during this process, the user can ask that a verifier.DAG be constructed to represent what has been seen so far.
